{
 "name": "RPlog_Party_Triggered",
 "title": "Party Triggered",
 "summary": "In his discreet, insect-snack-stocked office at the Tahn Consortium on Athaniss, the ex-Sector Authority businessman Malif Tal-Tahn engages the Kubaz fashion designer Zubindi Hakoon and his practical Pantoran assistant Veruca Violet to design an extravagant, provocative party. Malif lays out an unusual theme inspired by the wild-card legacy of the late scientist Basca Starker, musing about moving a party 'from beauty to beast' while keeping it enjoyable. With an open venue, unlimited budget from his successful mining operations, and creative free rein, Zubindi grows excited at the prospect of crafting the party of the year. The trio sketches out ideas, and Zubindi departs to scout galaxy-wide locations to fit Malif's dark vision.",
